### 4. List All Orders
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders?pageNumber=1&pageSize=20

### 5. List Orders by Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders?status=Pending

### 6. List Orders by Customer
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders?customerId=3fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa6

### 7. Get Order by ID (Replace with actual order ID from create)
@orderId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders/{{orderId}}

### 8. Get Order by ID (Not Found)
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders/99999999-9999-9999-9999-999999999999

### 9. Update Order Status (Valid)
@orderId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/orders/{{orderId}}/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "Confirmed"
}

